com.opengamma.strata.basics.market

Class MarketDataFeed

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.collect.type.TypedString<MarketDataFeed>
      • com.opengamma.strata.basics.market.MarketDataFeed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<MarketDataFeed>

    public final class MarketDataFeed
extends TypedString<MarketDataFeed>
    Identifies a feed of market data, for example Bloomberg or Reuters.

    A feed can represent the default source of data for a particular data provider, or it can represent a subset of the data from the provider, for example data from a specific broker published by Bloomberg. Therefore there can be multiple feeds providing data from a single physical market data system.
